---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer style="border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);margin-top:6rem;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;align-items:center;">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
          <span style="color:#c8a96e;font-size:1.125rem;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:0.2em;">NaNi</span>
          <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;">EXECUTION LAB</span>
        </div>
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;">
          データでプロセスを再設計し、価値を生む自律型仕組みを実現する。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:2rem;">
        <a href="/contact" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;transition:color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#c8a96e'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.3)'">CONTACT</a>
        <a href="/cases"   style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;transition:color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#c8a96e'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.3)'">事例</a>
        <a href="/blog"    style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-size:0.7rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;transition:color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#c8a96e'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255,255,255,0.3)'">BLOG</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Copyright -->
      <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-top:0.5rem;">
        © {year} NaNi Execution Lab. All Rights Reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
